[[!template id=ns:file]][[thumb|:HASTUschon_Logo.jpg]]**HASTUschon?** is a german site withe a wide variety of products an auction types like normal bid oder fixed price auctions with the possibility to use Bitcoins for paying.

Every product which uses the "HASTUschon-Treuhandservice" can be payed in Bitcoins.

##History

* The possibility for paying with Bitcoins started in June 2011.

